{"name": "requests-ntlm", "metadata": {"name": "requests-ntlm", "version": "1.3.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: ISC License (ISCL)", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/requests/requests-ntlm", "license": "ISC", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["cryptography", "pyspnego", "requests"], "summary": "This package allows for HTTP NTLM authentication using the requests library.", "upload_time": 1717977123}, "documentation": ["# requests-ntlm\n\n```{image} https://github.com/requests/requests-ntlm/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg\n:target: https://github.com/requests/requests-ntlm/actions/workflows/ci.yml\n```\n\nThis package allows for HTTP NTLM authentication using the requests library.\n\n## Usage\n\n`HttpNtlmAuth` extends requests `AuthBase`, so usage is simple:\n\n```python\nimport requests\nfrom requests_ntlm import HttpNtlmAuth\n\nrequests.get(\"http://ntlm_protected_site.com\",auth=HttpNtlmAuth('domain\\\\username','password'))\n```\n\n`HttpNtlmAuth` can be used in conjunction with a `Session` in order to\nmake use of connection pooling. Since NTLM authenticates connections,\nthis is more efficient. Otherwise, each request will go through a new\nNTLM challenge-response.\n\n```python\nimport requests\nfrom requests_ntlm import HttpNtlmAuth\n\nsession = requests.Session()\nsession.auth = HttpNtlmAuth('domain\\\\username','password')\nsession.get('http://ntlm_protected_site.com')\n```\n\n## Installation\n\n> pip install requests_ntlm\n\n## Requirements\n\n- [requests]\n- [pyspnego]\n\n## Authors\n\n- [Ben Toews]\n\n* [Ian Cordasco]\n\n- [Cory Benfield]\n\n[ben toews]: https://github.com/mastahyeti\n[cory benfield]: https://github.com/Lukasa\n[ian cordasco]: https://github.com/sigmavirus24\n[pyspnego]: https://github.com/jborean93/pyspnego/\n[requests]: https://github.com/kennethreitz/requests/\n"], "modules": [{"name": "requests_ntlm", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth", "xref": {"fqname": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm._auth_type_from_header", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "header", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Given a WWW-Authenticate or Proxy-Authenticate header, returns the\nauthentication type to use. We prefer NTLM over Negotiate if the server\nsuppports it."]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm._get_certificate_hash", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "certificate_der", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bytes | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.ShimSessionSecurity", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.ShimSessionSecurity.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "context", "type": {"name": "spnego.ContextProxy", "xref": {"fqname": "spnego.ContextProxy", "project": "pyspnego"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.ShimSessionSecurity.wrap", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.ShimSessionSecurity.unwrap", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "signature", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.ShimSessionSecurity.get_signature", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.ShimSessionSecurity.verify_signature", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "message", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "signature", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Shim used for backwards compatibility with ntlm-auth."]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth", "bases": ["AuthBase"], "methods": [{"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "username", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "password", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "session", "type": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "send_cbt", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Create an authentication handler for NTLM over HTTP.\n\n:param str username: Username in 'domain\\username' format\n:param str password: Password\n:param str session: Unused. Kept for backwards-compatibility.\n:param bool send_cbt: Will send the channel bindings over a HTTPS channel (Default: True)"]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth.retry_using_http_NTLM_auth", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "auth_header_field", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "auth_header", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "response", "type": {"name": "requests.Response", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.Response", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "auth_type", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "args", "type": {"name": "t.Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "requests.Response", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.Response", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth.response_hook", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "r", "type": {"name": "requests.Response", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.Response", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": {"name": "t.Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "requests.Response", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.Response", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["The actual hook handler."]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth._get_server_cert", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "response", "type": {"name": "requests.Response", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.Response", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bytes | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Get the certificate at the request_url and return it as a hash. Will get the raw socket from the\noriginal response from the server. This socket is then checked if it is an SSL socket and then used to\nget the hash of the certificate. The certificate hash is then used with NTLMv2 authentication for\nChannel Binding Tokens support. If the raw object is not a urllib3 HTTPReponse (default with requests)\nthen no certificate will be returned.\n\n```\nparam response\n\nThe original 401 response from the server\n\nreturn\n\nThe hash of the DER encoded certificate at the request_url or None if not a HTTPS endpoint\n```\n"]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.HttpNtlmAuth.__call__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "r", "type": {"name": "requests.PreparedRequest", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.PreparedRequest", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "requests.PreparedRequest", "xref": {"fqname": "requests.PreparedRequest", "project": "requests"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["HTTP NTLM Authentication Handler for Requests.\n\nSupports pass-the-hash."]}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.NoCertificateRetrievedWarning", "bases": ["Warning"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "requests_ntlm.requests_ntlm.UnknownSignatureAlgorithmOID", "bases": ["Warning"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}]}